{"tid":527734,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【連續兩年】淘寶又被美國列入賣假貨平台黑名單","createTime":"2018-01-13T04:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T04:11:20.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f8c1886575e2f664f31157de5ae90470407452","tid":527734,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180113/large/1515809550_b4a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180113%2Flarge%2F1515809550_b4a1.jpg&h=79f75a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴旗下淘寶網再被列入賣假貨的黑名單！美國貿易代表辦公室指，淘寶網站內仍有大量侵權物品銷售，於有關平台上進行知識權維護仍有不少挑戰，故將淘寶列入涉嫌銷售假貨購物平台的黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴則指出，美國貿易辦公室忽視公司維持知識產權的努力及成果，目前下架要求已減少25%，不少侵權貨品亦已被移走。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180113/57701898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180113%2F57701898&d=l4mTuajFObyFCLMSbUrGD9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=488a51f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180113%2F57701898&h=966c13db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180113/57701898</a>"}]}